{"tid":2211871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"燒炭自殺係咪會好快死","createTime":"2020-09-21T11:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T13:02:20.000Z","uid":329350,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"remark":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：\n[url]https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline[/url]","replies":[{"pid":"6f5a63a8fc795f795e536e2045b4236aaa6dedfb","tid":2211871,"uid":329350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"燒炭大概幾耐會死？<br />\n算唔算係無痛苦咁死"},{"pid":"13fcd381b380783d80ea7660e273df4e1b3bc744","tid":2211871,"uid":355310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"咩事唔開心講黎聽下"},{"pid":"88ace83c3ed2b1b1bcdb629bccbfde22d34dc6eb","tid":2211871,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"好耐架好辛苦<br />\n唔好諗"},{"pid":"0a23bd7cf4cd925c1ed003284ad54bf87b7b2bb2","tid":2211871,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:35:36.000Z","msg":"樓主想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc583aaab38c80d50a02f33091f0fd2328ae9b4","tid":2211871,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"好撚痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：喺地獄上緊連登"},{"pid":"bfeb9aec1a6a246d4dedf5c3abc4b3c7a46a118e","tid":2211871,"uid":366245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d01fd380c2b7c2df4ac919e4b8c2378a3aca02de","tid":2211871,"uid":223468,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"唔好問 唔好做 唔好諗"},{"pid":"7726748b0723bb4383ac99ca912cf4a995b99929","tid":2211871,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:23:01.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<br />\n雖然人生真係好艱難<br />\nwe all know it"},{"pid":"c1a3aa972243b4189673b320588fa9fc312cb837","tid":2211871,"uid":122513,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6f5a63a8fc795f795e536e2045b4236aaa6dedfb","tid":2211871,"uid":329350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"燒炭大概幾耐會死？<br />\n算唔算係無痛苦咁死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"&quot;警犬仆街&quot;，看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZojQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=3d954544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZojQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=06a8aa3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a>  ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n*由2020年10月5日起，『Chat窿』服務時段將作出以下調整︰星期一至五︰下午4時 - 凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期︰下午8時- 凌晨1時<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"09f0c199f6521ab8d7b45dd8cb73266224f95ba9","tid":2211871,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"你死咗，你個紅老母咪開心，你條氣順咩？<br />\n應該有咁長命得咁長命，要佢激到死為止"},{"pid":"db13ab589ba6f8e61f8240297148fe2c8435e06e","tid":2211871,"uid":36673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"千萬唔好燒炭，過程中醒會好痛苦<br />\n同埋腦缺過氧俾人救返喺一世.....<br />\n發生咗啲咩令你考慮要自殺<img src=